description:
Happy Friday. On today’s episode of Human Events Daily - The prosecution in the Kyle Rittenhouse Trial is caught TAMPERING with evidence, The Kyle Rittenhouse Trial has turned into a political show trial, The FBI leaks Project Veritas communications with lawyer to the NYT, and Scottsdale School Board made private Dossier on parents who oppose CRT.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
